1.0.name: wordpress/invoice-king-pro
1.0.description:
--

Stay up-to-date with the latest by following @kingproplugins on Twitter, KingProPlugins on Facebook or King Pro Plugins on Google+

--

Invoice King Pro makes creating and sending your invoices simple. The invoice creation interface gives you full control over every word on your invoice. Choose a different theme to give your invoices the look, style and layout that you want. If there isn't a layout that suits your needs, thats ok, it can be created! Themes are available on the King Pro Plugins website.

The Invoice King Pro settings area will allow you to set some data that will be consiste
